var book = {
	"name": "Zechariah",
	"numChapters": 14,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">1 </span>In the eighth month, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22880A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22880A\"></sup>in the second year of Darius, the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to the prophet <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22880B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22880B\"></sup>Zechariah, the son of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22880C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22880C\"></sup>Berechiah, son of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22880D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22880D\"></sup>Iddo, saying,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22881E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22881E\"></sup>“The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> was very angry with your fathers.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Therefore say to them, Thus declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22882F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22882F\"></sup>Return to me, says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22882G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22882G\"></sup>I will return to you, says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22883H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22883H\"></sup>Do not be like your fathers, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22883I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22883I\"></sup>to whom the former prophets cried out, ‘Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22883J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22883J\"></sup>Return from your evil ways and from your evil deeds.’ But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22883K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22883K\"></sup>they did not hear or pay attention to me, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Your fathers, where are they? And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22884L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22884L\"></sup>the prophets, do they live forever?",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22885M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22885M\"></sup>But my words and my statutes, which I commanded <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22885N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22885N\"></sup>my servants the prophets, did they not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22885O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22885O\"></sup>overtake your fathers? So they repented and said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22885P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22885P\"></sup>‘As the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts purposed to deal with us for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22885Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22885Q\"></sup>our ways and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22885R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22885R\"></sup>deeds, so has he dealt with us.’”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>On the twenty-fourth day of the eleventh month, which is the month of Shebat, in the second year of Darius, the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to the prophet <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22886S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22886S\"></sup>Zechariah, the son of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22886T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22886T\"></sup>Berechiah, son of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22886U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22886U\"></sup>Iddo, saying,",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“I saw in the night, and behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22887V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22887V\"></sup>a man riding on a red horse! He was standing among the myrtle trees in the glen, and behind him were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22887W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22887W\"></sup>red, sorrel, and white horses.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Then I said, ‘What are these, my lord?’ <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22888X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22888X\"></sup>The angel who talked with me said to me, ‘I will show you what they are.’",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>So <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22889Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22889Y\"></sup>the man who was standing among the myrtle trees answered, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22889Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22889Z\"></sup>‘These are they whom the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has sent to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22889AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22889AA\"></sup>patrol the earth.’",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And they answered <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22890AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22890AB\"></sup>the angel of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> who was standing among the myrtle trees, and said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22890AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22890AC\"></sup>‘We have patrolled the earth, and behold, all the earth <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22890AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22890AD\"></sup>remains at rest.’",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22891AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22891AE\"></sup>the angel of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22891AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22891AF\"></sup>‘O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22891AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22891AG\"></sup>how long will you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22891AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22891AH\"></sup>have no mercy on Jerusalem and the cities of Judah, against which you have been angry these <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22891AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22891AI\"></sup>seventy years?’",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> answered <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22892AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22892AJ\"></sup>gracious and comforting words to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22892AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22892AK\"></sup>the angel who talked with me.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>So <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22893AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22893AL\"></sup>the angel who talked with me said to me, ‘Cry out, Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22893AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22893AM\"></sup>I am exceedingly jealous for Jerusalem and for Zion.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22894AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22894AN\"></sup>And I am exceedingly angry with the nations that are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22894AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22894AO\"></sup>at ease; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22894AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22894AP\"></sup>for while I was angry but a little, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22894AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22894AQ\"></sup>they furthered the disaster.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Therefore, thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22895AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22895AR\"></sup>I have returned to Jerusalem with mercy; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22895AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22895AS\"></sup>my house shall be built in it, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22895AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22895AT\"></sup>the measuring line shall be stretched out over Jerusalem.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Cry out again, Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22896AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22896AU\"></sup>My cities shall again overflow with prosperity, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22896AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22896AV\"></sup>and the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will again comfort Zion and again <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22896AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22896AW\"></sup>choose Jerusalem.’”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup> And I lifted my eyes and saw, and behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22897AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22897AX\"></sup>four horns!",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>And I said to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22898AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22898AY\"></sup>the angel who talked with me, “What are these?” And he said to me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22898AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22898AZ\"></sup>“These are the horns that have scattered Judah, Israel, and Jerusalem.”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> showed me four craftsmen.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>And I said, “What are these coming to do?” He said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22900BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22900BA\"></sup>“These are the horns that scattered Judah, so that no one raised his head. And these have come <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22900BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22900BB\"></sup>to terrify them, to cast down the horns of the nations <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22900BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22900BC\"></sup>who lifted up their horns against the land of Judah to scatter it.”"
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">2 </span> And I lifted my eyes and saw, and behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22901A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22901A\"></sup>a man with a measuring line in his hand!",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Then I said, “Where are you going?” And he said to me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22902B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22902B\"></sup>“To measure Jerusalem, to see what is its width and what is its length.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22903C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22903C\"></sup>the angel who talked with me came forward, and another angel came forward to meet him",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>and said to him, “Run, say to that young man, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22904D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22904D\"></sup>‘Jerusalem shall be inhabited <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22904E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22904E\"></sup>as villages without walls, because of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22904F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22904F\"></sup>the multitude of people and livestock in it.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And I will be to her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22905G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22905G\"></sup>a wall of fire all around, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and I will be the glory in her midst.’”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Up! Up! <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22906H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22906H\"></sup>Flee from the land of the north, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>. For I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22906I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22906I\"></sup>spread you abroad as the four winds of the heavens, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22907J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22907J\"></sup>Up! Escape to Zion, you who dwell with the daughter of Babylon.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>For thus said the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, after his glory sent me to the nations who plundered you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22908K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22908K\"></sup>for he who touches you touches <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22908L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22908L\"></sup>the apple of his eye:",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22909M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22909M\"></sup>I will shake my hand over them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22909N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22909N\"></sup>and they shall become plunder for those who served them. Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22909O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22909O\"></sup>you will know that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts has sent me.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22910P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22910P\"></sup>Sing and rejoice, O daughter of Zion, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22910Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22910Q\"></sup>behold, I come <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22910R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22910R\"></sup>and I will dwell in your midst, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22911S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22911S\"></sup>And many nations shall join themselves to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> in that day, and shall be my people. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22911T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22911T\"></sup>And I will dwell in your midst, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22911U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22911U\"></sup>you shall know that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts has sent me to you.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22912V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22912V\"></sup>And the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will inherit Judah as his portion in the holy land, and will again <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22912W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22912W\"></sup>choose Jerusalem.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Be silent, all flesh, before the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, for he has roused himself from his holy dwelling."
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">3 </span>Then he showed me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22914A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22914A\"></sup>Joshua the high priest standing before the angel of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22914B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22914B\"></sup>Satan standing at his right hand to accuse him.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to Satan, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22915C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22915C\"></sup>“The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> rebuke you, O Satan! The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> who has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22915D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22915D\"></sup>chosen Jerusalem rebuke you! Is not this <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22915E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22915E\"></sup>a brand plucked from the fire?”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22916F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22916F\"></sup>Joshua was standing before the angel, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22916G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22916G\"></sup>clothed with filthy garments.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And the angel said to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22917H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22917H\"></sup>those who were standing before him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22917I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22917I\"></sup>“Remove the filthy garments from him.” And to him he said, “Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22917J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22917J\"></sup>I have taken your iniquity away from you, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22917K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22917K\"></sup>I will clothe you with pure vestments.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And I said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22918L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22918L\"></sup>“Let them put a clean turban on his head.” So they put a clean turban on his head and clothed him with garments. And the angel of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> was standing by.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And the angel of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> solemnly assured <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22919M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22919M\"></sup>Joshua,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts: If you will walk in my ways and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22920N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22920N\"></sup>keep my charge, then you shall <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22920O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22920O\"></sup>rule my house and have charge of my courts, and I will give you the right of access among <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22920P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22920P\"></sup>those who are standing here.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Hear now, O Joshua the high priest, you and your friends who sit before you, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22921Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22921Q\"></sup>they are men who are a sign: behold, I will bring <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22921R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22921R\"></sup>my servant <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22921S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22921S\"></sup>the Branch.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>For behold, on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22922T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22922T\"></sup>the stone that I have set before Joshua, on a single stone with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22922U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22922U\"></sup>seven eyes, I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22922V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22922V\"></sup>engrave its inscription, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22922W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22922W\"></sup>I will remove the iniquity of this land in a single day.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>In that day, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, every one of you will invite his neighbor to come <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22923X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22923X\"></sup>under his vine and under his fig tree.”"
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">4 </span>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22924A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22924A\"></sup>the angel who talked with me came again <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22924B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22924B\"></sup>and woke me, like a man who is awakened out of his sleep.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And he said to me, “What do you see?” I said, “I see, and behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22925C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22925C\"></sup>a lampstand all of gold, with a bowl on the top of it, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22925D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22925D\"></sup>seven lamps on it, with seven lips on each of the lamps that are on the top of it.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And there are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22926E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22926E\"></sup>two olive trees by it, one on the right of the bowl and the other on its left.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And I said to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22927F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22927F\"></sup>the angel who talked with me, “What are these, my lord?”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Then the angel who talked with me answered and said to me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22928G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22928G\"></sup>“Do you not know what these are?” I said, “No, my lord.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Then he said to me, “This is the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22929H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22929H\"></sup>Zerubbabel: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22929I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22929I\"></sup>Not by might, nor by power, but by my Spirit, says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Who are you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22930J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22930J\"></sup>O great mountain? Before <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22930K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22930K\"></sup>Zerubbabel <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22930L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22930L\"></sup>you shall become a plain. And he shall bring forward <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22930M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22930M\"></sup>the top stone amid shouts of ‘Grace, grace to it!’”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Then the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me, saying,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22932N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22932N\"></sup>“The hands of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22932O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22932O\"></sup>Zerubbabel have laid the foundation of this house; his hands shall also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22932P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22932P\"></sup>complete it. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22932Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22932Q\"></sup>Then you will know that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts has sent me to you.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22933R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22933R\"></sup>For whoever has despised the day of small things shall rejoice, and shall see <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22933S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22933S\"></sup>the plumb line in the hand of Zerubbabel.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22933T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22933T\"></sup>“These seven <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22933U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22933U\"></sup>are the eyes of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22933V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22933V\"></sup>which range through the whole earth.”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Then I said to him, “What are these <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22934W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22934W\"></sup>two olive trees on the right and the left of the lampstand?”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And a second time I answered and said to him, “What are these <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22935X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22935X\"></sup>two branches of the olive trees, which are beside the two golden pipes from which the golden oil is poured out?”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>He said to me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22936Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22936Y\"></sup>“Do you not know what these are?” I said, “No, my lord.”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Then he said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22937Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22937Z\"></sup>“These are the two anointed ones who stand by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22937AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22937AA\"></sup>the Lord of the whole earth.”"
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">5 </span>Again I lifted my eyes and saw, and behold, a flying <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22938A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22938A\"></sup>scroll!",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And he said to me, “What do you see?” I answered, “I see a flying <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22939B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22939B\"></sup>scroll. Its length is twenty cubits, and its width ten cubits.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Then he said to me, “This is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22940C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22940C\"></sup>the curse that goes out over the face of the whole land. For everyone who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22940D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22940D\"></sup>steals shall be cleaned out according to what is on one side, and everyone who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22940E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22940E\"></sup>swears falsely shall be cleaned out according to what is on the other side.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>I will send it out, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, and it shall enter the house of the thief, and the house of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22941F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22941F\"></sup>him who swears falsely by my name. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22941G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22941G\"></sup>it shall remain in his house and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22941H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22941H\"></sup>consume it, both timber and stones.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22942I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22942I\"></sup>Then the angel who talked with me came forward and said to me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22942J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22942J\"></sup>“Lift your eyes and see what this is that is going out.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And I said, “What is it?” He said, “This is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22943K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22943K\"></sup>the basket that is going out.” And he said, “This is their iniquity in all the land.”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And behold, the leaden cover was lifted, and there was a woman sitting in the basket!",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And he said, “This is Wickedness.” And he thrust her back into the basket, and thrust down <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22945L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22945L\"></sup>the leaden weight on its opening.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Then I lifted my eyes and saw, and behold, two women coming forward! <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22946M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22946M\"></sup>The wind was in their wings. They had wings like the wings of a stork, and they lifted up the basket between earth and heaven.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Then I said to the angel who talked with me, “Where are they taking the basket?”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>He said to me, “To the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22948N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22948N\"></sup>land of Shinar, to build a house for it. And when this is prepared, they will set the basket down there on its base.”"
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">6 </span>Again I lifted my eyes and saw, and behold, four chariots came out from between two mountains. And the mountains were mountains of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22949A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22949A\"></sup>bronze.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>The first chariot had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22950B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22950B\"></sup>red horses, the second <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22950C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22950C\"></sup>black horses,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>the third <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22951D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22951D\"></sup>white horses, and the fourth chariot dappled horses—all of them strong.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Then I answered and said to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22952E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22952E\"></sup>the angel who talked with me, “What are these, my lord?”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And the angel answered and said to me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22953F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22953F\"></sup>“These are going out to the four winds of heaven, after <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22953G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22953G\"></sup>presenting themselves before <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22953H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22953H\"></sup>the Lord of all the earth.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>The chariot with the black horses goes toward <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22954I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22954I\"></sup>the north country, the white ones go after them, and the dappled ones go toward <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22954J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22954J\"></sup>the south country.”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>When the strong horses came out, they were impatient to go and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22955K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22955K\"></sup>patrol the earth. And he said, “Go, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22955L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22955L\"></sup>patrol the earth.” <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22955M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22955M\"></sup>So they patrolled the earth.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Then he cried to me, “Behold, those who go toward <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22956N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22956N\"></sup>the north country have set my Spirit at rest in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22956O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22956O\"></sup>the north country.”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me:",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“Take from the exiles <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22958P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22958P\"></sup>Heldai, Tobijah, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22958Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22958Q\"></sup>Jedaiah, who have arrived from Babylon, and go the same day to the house of Josiah, the son of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22958R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22958R\"></sup>Zephaniah.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Take from them silver and gold, and make a crown, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22959S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22959S\"></sup>and set it on the head of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22959T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22959T\"></sup>Joshua, the son of Jehozadak, the high priest.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And say to him, ‘Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, “Behold, the man whose name is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22960U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22960U\"></sup>the Branch: for he shall branch out from his place, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22960V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22960V\"></sup>he shall build the temple of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22961W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22961W\"></sup>It is he who shall build the temple of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22961X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22961X\"></sup>and shall bear royal honor, and shall sit and rule on his throne. And there shall be a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22961Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22961Y\"></sup>priest on his throne, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22961Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22961Z\"></sup>and the counsel of peace shall be between them both.”’",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And the crown shall be in the temple of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22962AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22962AA\"></sup>a reminder to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22962AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22962AB\"></sup>Helem, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22962AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22962AC\"></sup>Tobijah, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22962AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22962AD\"></sup>Jedaiah, and Hen <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22962AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22962AE\"></sup>the son of Zephaniah.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22963AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22963AF\"></sup>“And those who are far off shall come and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22963AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22963AG\"></sup>help to build the temple of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22963AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22963AH\"></sup>And you shall know that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts has sent me to you. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22963AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22963AI\"></sup>And this shall come to pass, if you will diligently obey the voice of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God.”"
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">7 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22964A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22964A\"></sup>In the fourth year of King Darius, the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to Zechariah on the fourth day of the ninth month, which is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22964B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22964B\"></sup>Chislev.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Now the people of Bethel had sent Sharezer and Regem-melech and their men <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22965C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22965C\"></sup>to entreat the favor of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22966D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22966D\"></sup>saying to the priests of the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22966E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22966E\"></sup>the prophets, “Should I weep and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22966F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22966F\"></sup>abstain in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22966G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22966G\"></sup>the fifth month, as I have done for so many years?”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Then the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts came to me:",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“Say to all the people of the land and the priests, ‘When you fasted and mourned in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22968H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22968H\"></sup>the fifth month and in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22968I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22968I\"></sup>the seventh, for these <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22968J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22968J\"></sup>seventy years, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22968K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22968K\"></sup>was it <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22968L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22968L\"></sup>for me that you fasted?",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22969M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22969M\"></sup>And when you eat and when you drink, do you not eat for yourselves and drink for yourselves?",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22970N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22970N\"></sup>Were not these the words that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> proclaimed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22970O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22970O\"></sup>by the former prophets, when Jerusalem was inhabited and prosperous, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22970P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22970P\"></sup>with her cities around her, and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22970Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22970Q\"></sup>South and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22970R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22970R\"></sup>lowland were inhabited?’”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to Zechariah, saying,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22972S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22972S\"></sup>Render true judgments, show kindness and mercy to one another,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22973T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22973T\"></sup>do not oppress the widow, the fatherless, the sojourner, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22973U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22973U\"></sup>or the poor, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22973V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22973V\"></sup>let none of you devise evil against another in your heart.”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22974W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22974W\"></sup>they refused to pay attention <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22974X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22974X\"></sup>and turned a stubborn shoulder and stopped their ears that they might not hear.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22975Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22975Y\"></sup>They made their hearts diamond-hard <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22975Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22975Z\"></sup>lest they should hear the law and the words that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts had sent <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22975AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22975AA\"></sup>by his Spirit through <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22975AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22975AB\"></sup>the former prophets. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22975AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22975AC\"></sup>Therefore great anger came from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22976AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22976AD\"></sup>“As I called, and they would not hear, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22976AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22976AE\"></sup>so they called, and I would not hear,” says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22977AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22977AF\"></sup>“and I scattered them with a whirlwind among all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22977AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22977AG\"></sup>the nations that they had not known. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22977AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22977AH\"></sup>Thus the land they left was desolate, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22977AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22977AI\"></sup>so that no one went to and fro, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22977AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22977AJ\"></sup>and the pleasant land was made desolate.”"
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">8 </span>And the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts came, saying,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22979A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22979A\"></sup>I am jealous for Zion with great jealousy, and I am jealous for her with great wrath.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22980B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22980B\"></sup>I have returned to Zion and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22980C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22980C\"></sup>will dwell in the midst of Jerusalem, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22980D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22980D\"></sup>and Jerusalem shall be called the faithful city, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22980E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22980E\"></sup>and the mountain of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, the holy mountain.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22981F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22981F\"></sup>Old men and old women shall again sit in the streets of Jerusalem, each with staff in hand because of great age.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And the streets of the city shall be full of boys and girls playing in its streets.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22983G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22983G\"></sup>If it is marvelous in the sight of the remnant of this people in those days, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22983H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22983H\"></sup>should it also be marvelous in my sight, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts?",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts: Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22984I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22984I\"></sup>I will save my people <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22984J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22984J\"></sup>from the east country and from the west country,",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>and I will bring them to dwell in the midst of Jerusalem. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22985K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22985K\"></sup>And they shall be my people, and I will be their God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22985L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22985L\"></sup>in faithfulness and in righteousness.”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22986M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22986M\"></sup>“Let your hands be strong, you who in these days have been hearing these words from the mouth of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22986N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22986N\"></sup>the prophets who were present on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22986O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22986O\"></sup>the day that the foundation of the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts was laid, that the temple might be built.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>For before those days <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22987P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22987P\"></sup>there was no wage for man or any wage for beast, neither was there any safety from the foe for him who went out or came in, for I set every man against his neighbor.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>But now I will not deal with the remnant of this people as in the former days, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22989Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22989Q\"></sup>For there shall be a sowing of peace. The vine shall give its fruit, and the ground shall give its produce, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22989R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22989R\"></sup>and the heavens shall give their dew. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22989S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22989S\"></sup>And I will cause the remnant of this people to possess all these things.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22990T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22990T\"></sup>you have been a byword of cursing among the nations, O house of Judah and house of Israel, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22990U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22990U\"></sup>so will I save you, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22990V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22990V\"></sup>you shall be a blessing. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22990W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22990W\"></sup>Fear not, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22990X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22990X\"></sup>let your hands be strong.”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>For thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22991Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22991Y\"></sup>“As I purposed to bring disaster to you when your fathers provoked me to wrath, and I did not relent, says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts,",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>so again have I purposed in these days to bring good to Jerusalem and to the house of Judah; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22992Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22992Z\"></sup>fear not.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>These are the things that you shall do: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22993AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22993AA\"></sup>Speak the truth to one another; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22993AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22993AB\"></sup>render in your gates judgments <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22993AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22993AC\"></sup>that are true and make for peace;",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22994AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22994AD\"></sup>do not devise evil in your hearts against one another, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22994AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22994AE\"></sup>love no false oath, for all these things I hate, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>And the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts came to me, saying,",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts: The fast of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22996AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22996AF\"></sup>fourth month and the fast of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22996AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22996AG\"></sup>fifth and the fast of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22996AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22996AH\"></sup>seventh and the fast of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22996AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22996AI\"></sup>tenth shall be to the house of Judah <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22996AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22996AJ\"></sup>seasons of joy and gladness and cheerful feasts. Therefore love <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22996AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22996AK\"></sup>truth and peace.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts: Peoples shall yet come, even the inhabitants of many cities.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>The inhabitants of one city shall go to another, saying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22998AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22998AL\"></sup>‘Let us go at once <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22998AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22998AM\"></sup>to entreat the favor of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> and to seek the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts; I myself am going.’",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22999AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22999AN\"></sup>Many peoples and strong nations shall come to seek the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts in Jerusalem and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22999AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22999AO\"></sup>to entreat the favor of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts: In those days <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23000AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23000AP\"></sup>ten men <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23000AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23000AQ\"></sup>from the nations of every tongue shall take hold of the robe of a Jew, saying, ‘Let us go with you, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23000AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23000AR\"></sup>we have heard that God is with you.’”"
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">9 </span>The oracle of the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is against the land of Hadrachand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23001A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23001A\"></sup>Damascus is its resting place.For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has an eye on mankindand on all the tribes of Israel,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23002B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23002B\"></sup>and on Hamath also, which borders on it,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23002C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23002C\"></sup>Tyre and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23002D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23002D\"></sup>Sidon, though <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23002E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23002E\"></sup>they are very wise.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Tyre has built herself <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23003F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23003F\"></sup>a rampartand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23003G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23003G\"></sup>heaped up silver like dust,and fine gold like the mud of the streets.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>But behold, the Lord will strip her of her possessionsand strike down <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23004H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23004H\"></sup>her power on the sea,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23004I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23004I\"></sup>she shall be devoured by fire.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23005J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23005J\"></sup>Ashkelon shall see it, and be afraid;Gaza too, and shall writhe in anguish;Ekron also, because its hopes are confounded.The king shall perish from Gaza;Ashkelon shall be uninhabited;",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23006K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23006K\"></sup>a mixed people shall dwell in Ashdod,and I will cut off the pride of Philistia.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>I will take away <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23007L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23007L\"></sup>its blood from its mouth,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23007M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23007M\"></sup>its abominations from between its teeth;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23007N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23007N\"></sup>it too shall be a remnant for our God;it shall be like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23007O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23007O\"></sup>a clan in Judah,and Ekron shall be like the Jebusites.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23008P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23008P\"></sup>I will encamp at my house as a guard,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23008Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23008Q\"></sup>so that none shall march to and fro;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23008R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23008R\"></sup>no oppressor shall again march over them,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23008S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23008S\"></sup>for now I see with my own eyes.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23009T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23009T\"></sup>Rejoice greatly, O daughter of Zion!Shout aloud, O daughter of Jerusalem!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23009U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23009U\"></sup>Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23009V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23009V\"></sup>your king is coming to you;righteous and having salvation is he,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23009W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23009W\"></sup>humble and mounted on a donkey,on a colt, the foal of a donkey.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23010X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23010X\"></sup>I will cut off the chariot from Ephraimand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23010Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23010Y\"></sup>the war horse from Jerusalem;and the battle bow shall be cut off,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23010Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23010Z\"></sup>he shall speak peace to the nations;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23010AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23010AA\"></sup>his rule shall be from sea to sea,and from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23010AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23010AB\"></sup>the River to the ends of the earth.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>As for you also, because of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23011AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23011AC\"></sup>the blood of my covenant with you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23011AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23011AD\"></sup>I will set your prisoners free from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23011AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23011AE\"></sup>the waterless pit.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Return to your stronghold, O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23012AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23012AF\"></sup>prisoners of hope;today I declare that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23012AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23012AG\"></sup>I will restore to you double.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23013AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23013AH\"></sup>I have bent Judah as my bow;I have made Ephraim its arrow.I will stir up your sons, O Zion,against your sons, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23013AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23013AI\"></sup>O Greece,and wield you like a warrior's sword.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will appear over them,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23014AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23014AJ\"></sup>his arrow will go forth like lightning;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23014AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23014AK\"></sup>the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> will sound the trumpetand will march forth in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23014AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23014AL\"></sup>the whirlwinds <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23014AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23014AM\"></sup>of the south.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23015AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23015AN\"></sup>will protect them,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23015AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23015AO\"></sup>they shall devour, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23015AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23015AP\"></sup>and tread down the sling stones,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23015AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23015AQ\"></sup>they shall drink and roar as if drunk with wine,and be full like a bowl,drenched <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23015AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23015AR\"></sup>like the corners of the altar.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>On that day the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> their God will save them,as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23016AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23016AS\"></sup>the flock of his people;for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23016AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23016AT\"></sup>like the jewels of a crownthey shall shine on his land.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23017AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23017AU\"></sup>For how great is his goodness, and how great his beauty!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23017AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23017AV\"></sup>Grain shall make the young men flourish,and new wine the young women."
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">10 </span>Ask rain <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23018A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23018A\"></sup>from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>in the season of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23018B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23018B\"></sup>the spring rain,from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23018C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23018C\"></sup>who makes the storm clouds,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23018D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23018D\"></sup>he will give them showers of rain,to everyone the vegetation in the field.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23019E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23019E\"></sup>the household gods <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23019F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23019F\"></sup>utter nonsense,and the diviners see lies;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23019G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23019G\"></sup>they tell false dreamsand give empty consolation.Therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23019H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23019H\"></sup>the people wander like sheep;they are afflicted for lack of a shepherd.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23020I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23020I\"></sup>“My anger is hot against the shepherds,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23020J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23020J\"></sup>I will punish the leaders;for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23020K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23020K\"></sup>the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts cares for his flock, the house of Judah,and will make them like his majestic steed in battle.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>From him shall come <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23021L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23021L\"></sup>the cornerstone,from him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23021M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23021M\"></sup>the tent peg,from him the battle bow,from him every ruler—<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23021N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23021N\"></sup>all of them together.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>They shall be like mighty men in battle,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23022O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23022O\"></sup>trampling the foe in the mud of the streets;they shall fight because the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is with them,and they shall put to shame <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23022P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23022P\"></sup>the riders on horses.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23023Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23023Q\"></sup>“I will strengthen the house of Judah,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23023R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23023R\"></sup>I will save the house of Joseph.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23023S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23023S\"></sup>I will bring them back <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23023T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23023T\"></sup>because I have compassion on them,and they shall be as though I had not rejected them,for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23023U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23023U\"></sup>I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> their God and I will answer them.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Then Ephraim shall become like a mighty warrior,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23024V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23024V\"></sup>their hearts shall be glad as with wine.Their children shall see it and be glad;their hearts shall rejoice in the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23025W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23025W\"></sup>“I will whistle for them and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23025X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23025X\"></sup>gather them in,for I have redeemed them,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23025Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23025Y\"></sup>they shall be as many as they were before.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23026Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23026Z\"></sup>Though I scattered them among the nations,yet in far countries <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23026AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23026AA\"></sup>they shall remember me,and with their children they shall live and return.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23027AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23027AB\"></sup>I will bring them home from the land of Egypt,and gather them from Assyria,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23027AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23027AC\"></sup>I will bring them to the land of Gilead and to Lebanon,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23027AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23027AD\"></sup>till there is no room for them.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23028AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23028AE\"></sup>He shall pass through the sea of troublesand strike down the waves of the sea,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23028AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23028AF\"></sup>and all the depths of the Nile shall be dried up.The pride of Assyria shall be laid low,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23028AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23028AG\"></sup>the scepter of Egypt shall depart.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23029AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23029AH\"></sup>I will make them strong in the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23029AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23029AI\"></sup>they shall walk in his name,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>."
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">11 </span>Open your doors, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23030A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23030A\"></sup>O Lebanon,that the fire may devour your cedars!",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Wail, O cypress, for the cedar has fallen,for the glorious trees are ruined!Wail, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23031B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23031B\"></sup>oaks of Bashan,for the thick forest has been felled!",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>The sound of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23032C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23032C\"></sup>the wail of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23032D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23032D\"></sup>the shepherds,for their glory is ruined!The sound of the roar of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23032E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23032E\"></sup>the lions,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23032F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23032F\"></sup>for the thicket of the Jordan is ruined!",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Thus said the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> my God: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23033G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23033G\"></sup>“Become shepherd of the flock doomed to slaughter.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23034H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23034H\"></sup>Those who buy them slaughter them and go unpunished, and those who sell them say, ‘Blessed be the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23034I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23034I\"></sup>I have become rich,’ and their own shepherds have no pity on them.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23035J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23035J\"></sup>I will no longer have pity on the inhabitants of this land, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>. Behold, I will cause each of them to fall into the hand of his neighbor, and each into the hand of his king, and they shall crush the land, and I will deliver none from their hand.”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23036K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23036K\"></sup>So I became the shepherd of the flock doomed to be slaughtered by the sheep traders. And I took two staffs, one I named <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23036L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23036L\"></sup>Favor, the other I named <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23036M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23036M\"></sup>Union. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23036N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23036N\"></sup>And I tended the sheep.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>In one month <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23037O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23037O\"></sup>I destroyed the three shepherds. But I became impatient with them, and they also detested me.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>So I said, “I will not be your shepherd. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23038P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23038P\"></sup>What is to die, let it die. What is to be destroyed, let it be destroyed. And let those who are left devour the flesh of one another.”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And I took <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23039Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23039Q\"></sup>my staff Favor, and I broke it, annulling the covenant that I had made with all the peoples.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>So it was annulled on that day, and the sheep traders, who were watching me, knew that it was the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Then I said to them, “If it seems good to you, give me my wages; but if not, keep them.” And they weighed out as my wages <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23041R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23041R\"></sup>thirty pieces of silver.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me, “Throw it to the potter”—<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23042S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23042S\"></sup>the lordly price at which I was priced by them. So I took the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23042T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23042T\"></sup>thirty pieces of silver and threw them into the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, to the potter.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Then I broke <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23043U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23043U\"></sup>my second staff Union, annulling the brotherhood between Judah and Israel.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me, “Take once more the equipment of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23044V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23044V\"></sup>a foolish shepherd.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>For behold, I am raising up in the land a shepherd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23045W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23045W\"></sup>who does not care for those being destroyed, or seek the young or heal the maimed or nourish the healthy, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23045X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23045X\"></sup>devours the flesh of the fat ones, tearing off even their hoofs.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23046Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23046Y\"></sup>“Woe to my worthless shepherd,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23046Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23046Z\"></sup>who deserts the flock!May the sword strike his armand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23046AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23046AA\"></sup>his right eye!Let his arm be wholly withered,his right eye utterly blinded!”"
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">12 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23047A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23047A\"></sup>The oracle of the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> concerning Israel: Thus declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23047B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23047B\"></sup>who stretched out the heavens and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23047C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23047C\"></sup>founded the earth and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23047D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23047D\"></sup>formed the spirit of man within him:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Behold, I am about to make Jerusalem <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23048E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23048E\"></sup>a cup of staggering to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23048F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23048F\"></sup>all the surrounding peoples. The siege of Jerusalem <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23048G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23048G\"></sup>will also be against Judah.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23049H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23049H\"></sup>On that day I will make Jerusalem a heavy stone for all the peoples. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23049I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23049I\"></sup>All who lift it will surely hurt themselves. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23049J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23049J\"></sup>all the nations of the earth will gather against it.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23050K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23050K\"></sup>On that day, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23050L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23050L\"></sup>I will strike every horse <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23050M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23050M\"></sup>with panic, and its rider <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23050N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23050N\"></sup>with madness. But for the sake of the house of Judah I will keep my eyes open, when I strike every horse of the peoples <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23050O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23050O\"></sup>with blindness.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Then the clans of Judah shall say to themselves, ‘The inhabitants of Jerusalem have strength through the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, their God.’",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23052P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23052P\"></sup>“On that day I will make the clans of Judah <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23052Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23052Q\"></sup>like a blazing pot in the midst of wood, like a flaming torch among sheaves. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23052R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23052R\"></sup>they shall devour to the right and to the left all the surrounding peoples, while <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23052S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23052S\"></sup>Jerusalem shall again be inhabited in its place, in Jerusalem.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“And the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will give salvation to the tents of Judah first, that the glory of the house of David and the glory of the inhabitants of Jerusalem may not surpass that of Judah.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23054T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23054T\"></sup>On that day <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23054U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23054U\"></sup>the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will protect the inhabitants of Jerusalem, so that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23054V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23054V\"></sup>the feeblest among them on that day shall be like David, and the house of David shall be like God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23054W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23054W\"></sup>like the angel of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, going before them.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23055X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23055X\"></sup>And on that day <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23055Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23055Y\"></sup>I will seek to destroy all the nations that come against Jerusalem.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23056Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23056Z\"></sup>I will pour out on the house of David and the inhabitants of Jerusalem a spirit of grace and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23056AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23056AA\"></sup>pleas for mercy, so that, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23056AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23056AB\"></sup>when they look on me, on him whom they have pierced, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23056AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23056AC\"></sup>they shall mourn for him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23056AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23056AD\"></sup>as one mourns for an only child, and weep bitterly over him, as one weeps over a firstborn.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23057AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23057AE\"></sup>On that day <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23057AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23057AF\"></sup>the mourning in Jerusalem will be as great <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23057AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23057AG\"></sup>as the mourning for Hadad-rimmon in the plain of Megiddo.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>The land shall mourn, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23058AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23058AH\"></sup>each family by itself: the family of the house of David by itself, and their wives by themselves; the family of the house of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23058AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23058AI\"></sup>Nathan by itself, and their wives by themselves;",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>the family of the house of Levi by itself, and their wives by themselves; the family of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23059AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23059AJ\"></sup>the Shimeites by itself, and their wives by themselves;",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>and all the families that are left, each by itself, and their wives by themselves."
		},
		"13": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">13 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23061A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23061A\"></sup>“On that day there shall be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23061B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23061B\"></sup>a fountain opened for the house of David and the inhabitants of Jerusalem, to cleanse them from sin and uncleanness.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23062C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23062C\"></sup>on that day, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23062D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23062D\"></sup>I will cut off the names of the idols from the land, so that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23062E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23062E\"></sup>they shall be remembered no more. And also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23062F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23062F\"></sup>I will remove from the land the prophets and the spirit of uncleanness.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And if anyone again prophesies, his father and mother who bore him will say to him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23063G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23063G\"></sup>‘You shall not live, for you speak lies in the name of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.’ And his father and mother who bore him shall pierce him through when he prophesies.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“On that day <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23064H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23064H\"></sup>every prophet will be ashamed of his vision when he prophesies. He will not put on a hairy cloak in order to deceive,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>but he will say, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23065I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23065I\"></sup>‘I am no prophet, I am a worker of the soil, for a man sold me in my youth.’",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And if one asks him, ‘What are these wounds on your back?’ he will say, ‘The wounds I received in the house of my friends.’",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“Awake, O sword, against <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23067J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23067J\"></sup>my shepherd,against the man who stands next to me,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23067K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23067K\"></sup>“Strike the shepherd, and the sheep will be scattered;I will turn my hand against the little ones.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>In the whole land, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,two thirds shall be cut off and perish,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23068L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23068L\"></sup>and one third shall be left alive.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23069M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23069M\"></sup>I will put this third into the fire,and refine them as one refines silver,and test them as gold is tested.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23069N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23069N\"></sup>They will call upon my name,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23069O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23069O\"></sup>I will answer them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23069P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23069P\"></sup>I will say, ‘They are my people’;and they will say, ‘The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is my God.’”"
		},
		"14": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">14 </span>Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23070A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23070A\"></sup>a day is coming for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, when the spoil taken from you will be divided in your midst.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23071B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23071B\"></sup>I will gather all the nations against Jerusalem to battle, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23071C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23071C\"></sup>the city shall be taken <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23071D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23071D\"></sup>and the houses plundered <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23071E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23071E\"></sup>and the women raped. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23071F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23071F\"></sup>Half of the city shall go out into exile, but the rest of the people shall not be cut off from the city.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23072G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23072G\"></sup>Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will go out and fight against those nations as when he fights on a day of battle.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23073H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23073H\"></sup>On that day his feet shall stand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23073I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23073I\"></sup>on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23073J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23073J\"></sup>the Mount of Olives that lies before Jerusalem on the east, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23073K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23073K\"></sup>the Mount of Olives shall be split in two from east to west by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23073L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23073L\"></sup>a very wide valley, so that one half of the Mount shall move northward, and the other half southward.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And you shall flee to the valley of my mountains, for the valley of the mountains shall reach to Azal. And you shall flee as you fled from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23074M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23074M\"></sup>the earthquake in the days of Uzziah king of Judah. Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> my God will come, and all the holy ones with him.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23075N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23075N\"></sup>On that day <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23075O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23075O\"></sup>there shall be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23075P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23075P\"></sup>no light, cold, or frost.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23076Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23076Q\"></sup>And there shall be a unique day, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23076R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23076R\"></sup>which is known to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, neither day nor night, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23076S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23076S\"></sup>at evening time there shall be light.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23077T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23077T\"></sup>On that day <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23077U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23077U\"></sup>living waters shall flow out from Jerusalem, half of them to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23077V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23077V\"></sup>the eastern sea and half of them to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23077W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23077W\"></sup>the western sea. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23077X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23077X\"></sup>It shall continue in summer as in winter.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23078Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23078Y\"></sup>the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will be king over all the earth. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23078Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23078Z\"></sup>On that day the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23078AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23078AA\"></sup>one and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23078AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23078AB\"></sup>his name one.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23079AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23079AC\"></sup>The whole land shall be turned into a plain from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23079AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23079AD\"></sup>Geba to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23079AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23079AE\"></sup>Rimmon south of Jerusalem. But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23079AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23079AF\"></sup>Jerusalem shall remain aloft <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23079AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23079AG\"></sup>on its site from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23079AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23079AH\"></sup>the Gate of Benjamin to the place of the former gate, to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23079AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23079AI\"></sup>the Corner Gate, and from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23079AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23079AJ\"></sup>the Tower of Hananel to the king's winepresses.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And it shall be inhabited, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23080AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23080AK\"></sup>there shall never again be a decree of utter destruction. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23080AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23080AL\"></sup>Jerusalem shall dwell in security.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And this shall be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23081AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23081AM\"></sup>the plague with which the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will strike all the peoples that wage war against Jerusalem: their flesh will rot while they are still standing on their feet, their eyes will rot in their sockets, and their tongues will rot in their mouths.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23082AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23082AN\"></sup>on that day a great panic from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> shall fall on them, so that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23082AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23082AO\"></sup>each will seize the hand of another, and the hand of the one will be raised against the hand of the other.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Even <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23083AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23083AP\"></sup>Judah will fight at Jerusalem. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23083AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23083AQ\"></sup>the wealth of all the surrounding nations shall be collected, gold, silver, and garments in great abundance.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23084AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23084AR\"></sup>a plague like this plague shall fall on the horses, the mules, the camels, the donkeys, and whatever beasts may be in those camps.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Then everyone who survives of all the nations that have come against Jerusalem <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23085AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23085AS\"></sup>shall go up year after year to worship <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23085AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23085AT\"></sup>the King, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23085AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23085AU\"></sup>to keep <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23085AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23085AV\"></sup>the Feast of Booths.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>And if <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23086AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23086AW\"></sup>any of the families of the earth do not go up to Jerusalem to worship <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23086AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23086AX\"></sup>the King, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23086AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23086AY\"></sup>there will be no rain on them.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>And if the family of Egypt does not go up and present themselves, then on them there shall be no rain; there shall be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23087AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23087AZ\"></sup>the plague with which the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> afflicts the nations that do not go up <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23087BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23087BA\"></sup>to keep the Feast of Booths.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>This shall be the punishment to Egypt and the punishment to all the nations that do not go up <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23088BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23088BB\"></sup>to keep the Feast of Booths.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23089BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23089BC\"></sup>on that day there shall be inscribed on the bells of the horses, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23089BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23089BD\"></sup>“Holy to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.” And the pots in the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> shall be as the bowls before the altar.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>And every pot in Jerusalem and Judah shall be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23090BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23090BE\"></sup>holy to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, so that all who sacrifice may come and take of them and boil the meat of the sacrifice in them. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23090BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23090BF\"></sup>there shall no longer be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23090BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23090BG\"></sup>a trader in the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-23090BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-23090BH\"></sup>on that day."
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;